      <title>०७४ दुर्योधनानुरोधः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/02_sabhAparva/10_anudyUtaparva/01_anudyUtam/074_duryodhanAnurodhaH/</link>
